'''A-3P0''' was a [[3PO-series protocol droid/Legends|3PO]] series [[Protocol droid/Legends|protocol droid]] serving as an administrator in the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] base on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Entooine]] during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. He welcomed the group of Rebels to the [[Entooine Rebel outpost|base]] who went on to help the native [[Askhew]] stop [[Jowart Typok]] from hunting the [[blue bantha]]s.

